dc_title_s: Lidar-Derived 45-cm Bare Earth DEM (m) for Taylor County, WI 2024
dc_description_s: This data represents a Lidar-derived 45-cm Bare Earth Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for Taylor County, Wisconsin in 2024.This dataset has elevation values in meter and is in the WTM coordinate system: EPSG 3071. A DEM represents the bare-Earth surface, removing all natural and built features.
uw_supplemental_s: Detailed metadata for the tiles used to create this countywide file:https://web.s3.wisc.edu/wsco-wisconsinview/lidar/Taylor/Taylor_2024_3DEP_Delivery/Metadata/Metadata.zip.
